{"tid":1514194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"休班警今年2月涉藏K仔被捕 警今落案控藏毒明提堂","createTime":"2019-08-28T15:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:02:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b98dc97ab18764097dccc20b19ad3931553de259","tid":1514194,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"46歲姓陳的警員，於今年2月21日休班期間，被警方在屯門龍門路進行打擊毒品行動時，揭發身上藏有1.65克、總值約660元的K仔，涉嫌藏毒被捕。警方調查多時，至今晚9時許，警方稱經調查及諮詢法律意見後，陳男被控一項藏毒罪，案件將於明日上午在屯門裁判法院提堂。"},{"pid":"a688c30032b3c6a008db228fd6b430790d5e1859","tid":1514194,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求入黎幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"425c383077567a60214bd8b4b9b20de7e7de8f57","tid":1514194,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"警犬要大清洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fce706a6ed13a4d4a8cab382880395b2cb208b","tid":1514194,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"0ef88fdb88fba6ac46dcaced4396d7c4901e488d","tid":1514194,"uid":14690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"捉得自己友<br />\n梗係有d野"},{"pid":"2098e1054dee6d8aa13898ee3e0c57ea49479142","tid":1514194,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef88fdb88fba6ac46dcaced4396d7c4901e488d","tid":1514194,"uid":14690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"捉得自己友<br />\n梗係有d野"},"citedBy":0